text: Kecskemét is a city in Hungary. It is located in the central part of the country. It is the eighth largest city of Hungary by population.Detailed Gazetteer of Hungary Retrieved 6 August 2018 The name of the city is derived from the word kecske which means "goat" in Hungarian language. == References == == Other websites == *Official website of Kecskemét Category:Cities in Hungary Category:Bács-Kiskun County
